material   0 0 0  0.2 0.2 0.2  0 0 0  0.8 0.8 0.8  0 0 0  0 1.2 0
material   0 0 0  0.2 0.2 0.2  0 0 0  0.8 0.8 0.8  0 0 0  0 1.3 0

# Four spheres touching one another
sphere   0   0  0 -2  2   
sphere   1  -1 -1  0  1   
